        {
            "title": "港股午後跌幅收窄至91點   藥業股揚升   阿里跌幅收窄",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後跌幅收窄，最高見23362點﹐跌幅收窄至91點或0.39%，突破上午高位，現報23337點，跌115點或0.49%。     </p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數報5279點，跌18點或0.35% ; 恒生國企指數報8467點，跌41點或0.49%。 </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市現成交1500.56億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)跌幅收窄至3.88%，報123.9元，仍為表現最差藍籌股    ; 騰訊(00700)跌1.26%，報509元; 美團(03690)跌2.95%，報131.4元。  </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">網易(09999)升幅擴大，升12.31%，報188.8元，見3年高，為表現最佳藍籌股。      </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥業股向好，中生製藥(01177)升3.33%，報4.03元 ; 翰森製藥(03692)升3.32%，報23.35元 ; 石藥(01093)升2.98%，報5.88元 ; 百濟神州(06160)憧憬染藍，升4.05%，報138.9元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211)升3.81%，報436.4元 ; 惟小鵬(09868)跌2.29%，報79.05元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14934114-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84%e8%87%b391%e9%bb%9e-%e8%97%a5%e6%a5%ad%e8%82%a1%e6%8f%9a%e5%8d%87-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-6.jpg.webp",
