            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台灣股市尾市造好。加權指數收市報21843點，升113點，升幅0.52%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數本周累計升逾4%。</p>\n</div>",
