        },
        {
            "title": "港元拆息大多反彈　1個月拆息回升至1.35厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14930704&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息大多回升，但升幅有限。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">1個月拆息反彈2.1個基點，結束7日跌勢，升至1.35厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜拆息升至約0.058厘，3個月拆息升至約2.12厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">只有兩星期拆息持續下跌，再跌2.7個基點，報大約0.77厘，連跌8日累計跌3.3厘。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14930704-%e6%b8%af%e5%85%83%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%a4%a7%e5%a4%9a%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88%e3%80%801%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%8b%86%e6%81%af%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87%e8%87%b31-35%e5%8e%98-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source_licensed_HKD_shutterstock-2.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 10:26:19",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "喜韻708萬元成交 原業主持貨10年帳面獲利約81.5萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14928318&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 150px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">香港置業西九龍深水埗分行日前促成一宗該屋苑的買賣成交，外區客以約708萬元購入2房單位，實用呎價約13992元，屬市價成交。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述單位為喜韻1座中層C室，實用面積約506平方呎，屬2房間隔，向西南望球場景，單位原業主以730萬元放盤約2星期後獲外區客洽詢，雙方經議價後以708萬元易手，實用呎價約13,992元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">資料顯示，業主於2015年1月以約626.5萬元購入上述單位，是次易手，原業主帳面獲利約81.5萬元離場。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14928318-%e5%96%9c%e9%9f%bb708%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e5%8e%9f%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a810%e5%b9%b4%e5%b8%b3%e9%9d%a2%e7%8d%b2%e5%88%a9%e7%b4%8481-5%e8%90%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-16 10:26:21",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
